Dominique Farrugia https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dominique_Farrugia 0 Dominique Farrugia (born 2 September 1962) is a French actor, film director, screenwriter, producer and humorist. He is a member and founder of the group of comedians Les Nuls alongside Alain Chabat and Chantal Lauby.
